snippet.title: ARMY OF THE CHRIST | Official Trailer | SWJC FILMS
snippet.description:
Written and Directed by Joshua Samuel, Army of the Christ is a groundbreaking Gospel feature film presented by SWJC FILMS — marking Pakistan’s first-ever Gospel cinematic experience.

The film stars Mathew Javed, Joshua Samuel, Khurram Patras, Mehran Zaib, Elishba Samuel, Sohail Waris, Shahbaz Gulzar, Yashwa Akram, and Rachel Mehran. 

Army of the Christ is inspired by an imaginary depiction of Matthew 24 from the Bible — a cinematic vision brought to life to inspire and awaken believers to rise and stand strong as The Army of the Christ.

Produced by Pastor Samuel Payara and captured through the lens of Director of Photography Sohail Joseph, the film blends faith, emotion, and cinematic excellence to create a historic milestone in Pakistan’s film industry — a bold step towards Gospel storytelling on the big screen.

Balancing the demands of his high-stakes job and his family, life proves increasingly challenging as Srikant navigates dangerous missions against terrorists while trying to be a present husband and father. snippet.title: Fire And Water: Making The Avatar Films - Official 'Streaming Now on Disney+' Trailer
snippet.description:
Take a look at the 'Streaming Now on Disney+' Trailer for Fire And Water: Making The Avatar Films, a behind-the-scenes look at the making of the Avatar films. Explore the process of developing Avatar: The Way of Water and a first look at the upcoming Avatar: Fire and Ash with Fire And Water: Making The Avatar Films, streaming now on Disney+.

The two-part documentary details the filmmaker's travels from Manhattan Beach, San Pedro, Shasta Lake, and the Channel Islands to the Bahamas, Hawaii, and New Zealand, to follow the cast and below-the-line team as they work to hone and perfect the techniques of underwater performance capture technology and learn to free dive in a massive, state-of-the-art 680,000-gallon water tank.

Fire And Water: Making The Avatar Films is streaming now exclusively on Disney+.
